const CURRENT_YEAR = new Date().getUTCFullYear()
---
<GlobalLayout title="contact me - cynthia's website">
	<PageHeader>Contact me</PageHeader>
	<main>
		<Section>
			Want to contact me? You can either reach me on one of my <a href='/socials'>socials</a>, or shoot me an
			email if you're more into old-school tech.
		</Section>
		<Section title='Email'>
			<p>
				Emails in {CURRENT_YEAR}?? Yeah. I read these, and I even (mostly) reply to them!
				Except if you're sending me weird stuff or spam.
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<a href='mailto:cynthia@cynthia.dev' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>cynthia@cynthia.dev</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href='mailto:cyyynthia@borkenware.com' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>cyyynthia@borkenware.com</a>
					for professional inquiries
				</li>
			</ul>
		</Section>
		<Section title='PGP'>
			<p>
				You can use PGP to encrypt your emails if you want. Make sure your public key is available somewhere,
				or I'll have to reply in boring plaintext...
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>key: <a href='/pgp.txt' target='_blank'>https://cynthia.dev/pgp.txt</a></li>
				<li>fingerprint: <code>FDDF 5DD9 34DC 5814 6C8B 3E8B CB56 1F74 DCEA E23B</code></li>
			</ul>
		</Section>
	</main>
</GlobalLayout>

<style>
	code {
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}
</style>
